{"tid":1944679,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何wayne 對現今換人名額制度既建議","createTime":"2020-03-26T14:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T14:32:56.000Z","uid":158145,"like":16,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"db13ab544ef0f1ca65517ac1cf48db8ee2c3eb28","tid":1944679,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"球隊有時會遇上比賽早段因為球員受傷問題，導致換人方面欠缺彈性，令戰術執行難以發揮<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，何蛇希望改革現今換人名額制度既不足<br />\n<br />\n以英超為例，每隊球隊要打38場比賽（每場有3個換人名額），等於有38x3=114個換人名額<br />\n<br />\n建議中114個名額可以由領隊彈性使用，佢地可以決定呢114個名額點用<br />\n<br />\n例如：可以由一開季就每場換6個人，半季就用哂啲換人名額，下半季就唔換得<br />\n<br />\n總之114個名額自己分配，想換就換，只要唔可以超出114次換人次數"},{"pid":"ae3aabb1be162f2bc97c3897b6826107458fe85e","tid":1944679,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8f1c60d59abbfcccdef4c81dbc998b074c959ae","tid":1944679,"uid":154406,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"傷病係比賽嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599a8098bb0f0b3d929249126a881eded4bd6823","tid":1944679,"uid":1977,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"分上下半季上限好d<br />\n下半季無得換人就真係柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606b41ce3d82fcc8a75fa1f1bf84e5b2026fa889","tid":1944679,"uid":158145,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"599a8098bb0f0b3d929249126a881eded4bd6823","tid":1944679,"uid":1977,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"分上下半季上限好d<br />\n下半季無得換人就真係柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"咁冇人叫個領隊一次過換哂啲人......."},{"pid":"977597010c63b6dff796180adc4342ea6953c911","tid":1944679,"uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"何蛇有啲料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/